title: Going Dominican!
itunes:title: Going Dominican!
description: We end summer with a BANG as master blender and cigar maker Jose Dominque drops by The Cigar Authority, and we smoke the Jose Dominique natural and maduro. Later in the show... the reveal of the real Boston strangler? It's time for the finer things in life... It's time for The Cigar Authority!
